5.text: "Neduntheev" is an island of the Northern Province. It is also known by its Dutch name Delft. It is an island located in the Palk Strait. The island's area is 50 km² and it is roughly oval-shaped. Neduntheev is a flat island surrounded by shallow waters and beaches of coral chunks and sand.
